<p><u><font size="7" face="Times New Roman">Expressive power</font></u></p>
<p ALIGN="JUSTIFY"><i><font size="5" face="Agency FB">Ability to cover a broad 
range of temporal scenarios required by the author.</font></i></p>
<p ALIGN="JUSTIFY"><font size="5" face="Agency FB">A formal approach to define expressive power.
</font> </p>
